            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>CTR measures clicks divided by impressions. Conversion rate measures completed actions (purchases, signups) divided by clicks. A high CTR with a low conversion rate usually means the ad or listing overpromised.</p></div></div>
